# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Pipeline working directory — every file under in-progress/ is transient
# telemetry/state. archiveFeatureFiles() moves the keepers to
# archive/features/<slug>/ at publish-pr time, so they land on the PR from
# there. Only README.md (folder docs) and *_SPEC.md (human-authored feature
# input) are tracked.
in-progress/*
!in-progress/README.md
!in-progress/*_SPEC.md
